<br>
Post Kunark, the new tune is &quot;Best toe-to-toe damage dealers.&quot;<br>
<br>
Kind of subtle, but the implication is that Rogues now deal the best melee damage -- if played well.<br>
<br>
The monk quest seems to start at the Library of Erudin, however this is an odd circumstance since Iksar monks are killed on sight there.  The Book of Immortals that you give to the fella there leads to the delivery of a note to another Erudite (in OOT).  He demands proof of your skill (i.e. your Robe of the Whistling Fists.  As if he couldn't see it.  Duh.)  Hand this to him and he will then reward you a book about the Celestial Fists (illegible).  This book, when handed to Keraian (monk NPC in Trakanon's Teeth), causes him to attack, however the book instantly returns to your inventory when he does.<br>
<br>
Killing him causes him to encourage you to visit an Astral Projection in Lake of Ill Omen.  Killing the Astral Projection causes it to tell you to brace yourself -- then nothing happens.<br>
<br>
Odds are, despite everything Abashi claims, this quest is busted. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=97.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=85.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.threadControl?topicID=92.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=92.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=92.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisroleplaying">The Tavern (Roleplaying)<option value="brellserilisfrm66">Rants Link<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilisfrm55">Fellowship of Guilds (Guildchat)<option value="brellserilisfrm64">Archived Threads<option value="brellserilisbrellslairadminonly">Brell's Lair (Admin only)<option value="brellserilismeleetalk">Tome: Races and Classes 